lines.value: kpnmnnh xaah 17 зyyhы эuэc xyptэn tycran mockbarnnh opwnh cyyryaaa honoonox aюyn ba зyyh europe a yyxan эpx p xэbээp bancah boonыh aanpantyyaыh uybpana зyyh europe pyy aanpy bancah
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: ypa europe a spain h фnnnnn ii p led cah , catholic xyyhyyannh эbcэn , mediterranean aanana ocmah h tэhrncnnh uэprnnh xyynnr yryncrэx xonboo banryyncah
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: lepanto h tynaaha ocmah-h фnot aээp tэahnn rnant ocmah h rnaraawryn bananыh зypart ranxantan uoxnnt bancah

lines.value: xэann tnnm bonoby tyyxyna ohooaop bapnnrыh ohaopt byx oaop wnhэ ycah ohrouыr эprэx constantinople h boomtyyatan , hanm opynh yennh galleasses r bartaaxыh onponuooroop 250 aananh arnan фnotыr xnncэh rnaranыh зypraah capыh aotopt , tэmunnnh bэnэrannnh ba yryn rr xatyy uэprnnh ytrыr ohuonho
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: venetian h canatan xэnэnuyynэryyaэa ocmah grand vizier in capturing cyprus from you

lines.value: we have cut off one of your arms in defeating our fleet you have merely shaved off our beard : tannbapnacah

lines.value: ocmah h tэhrncnnh uэprnnh xanx 1573 a эhx tanbah rэpээha rapыh ycэr зypax r venice r rtracah ba ocmah ymapa aфpnkt tэahnn banpnanыr bэxkyynэx ba hэmэraэk yaacah.xэann tnnm bonoby , typwnaratan tэhrncnnh uэprnnh oфnuepyya ba aananyna bancah юyr conbk bonoxryn banha
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: lepanto h tэpnnh tэmuэn tэpnnr typrэh conbcoh ohrouhyyaыh xoxnpnooc typwnaratan aknnnax xyynhr copoxoa ocmah h xap xox ohro a xon nnyy xopton bancah.эcpэrээp , зobxoh xybnnh uanзyyaыh omyna tobnopox xapbuahryn knknr tэmunyyaээp tэmaэrnэcэh , habsburg h xnn bonomknnh yaaah xnna cyypbwcah.vienna ottoman h apmn cyynnnh hampыh campaigning h amtnary pyy omho xabap yeэp constantinople c karcax tэp xamrnnh xonыh uэrnnr tэmaэrnэcэh , pre mechanized hac yea : myxapaan эhrnnh raзap зynh xrзraapyyaыr xapyyncah ba habsburg h xamraanantyyaыh xatyypax yypyyncah.tэp bac persia h safavids , opconaoohtэn ncnamыh yncыh эcpэr bycaa ba , austrians h эcpэr hэr : 2 oop фpohtyyaыr aэmknx xэpэruээrээp empire a tobor yypyyncah bэpxwээnyyannr xapyyncah.bannaaahы tanbapt , tэp эзэht rypэh-h xyytэn tэnэxnnr orcoh wnhэynэntээp uэprnnh texhonorna europeans cycэrtэn ba oюyhы conservatism ypryynax зorcoocoh ottomans aakmaap apa yhacah.uэprnnh xybbcrana european uэprnnh taktnkyya ba зэbcэrt oopynontyya uэprnnh xonboraon anaax annrah ynypyyncэh aanpantnnr sipahi h mopnh uэpэrt yypyyncah.habsburg austria эcpэr ypt aanh rant зэbcryyatэn equipped cah rbrah uэprnnh nx toohyyaыh xэpэruээr bnn bonrocoh.эhэ janissary h kopnycыh toohyyaaa yyxan ocont ba эncyynэxnnh boanorыh ampantaa honooncoh.эhэ зacrnnh raзap bypэh epaoo ort эhэ bytэh uэr yeэp xapny oroxryn rэby tan bapnnacah , kopnycыh aotop nnt , yp honoohnn aytaraan , caxnnra batryn banaan-h bэpxwээnyyaэa tycancah
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: europeans p rant зэbcryyannh hэmэracэh xэpэrnээtэn wynyyh taktnkyya cyyna aapaa ba uypxan ba ohoor xorknn xэt yxэxээp ottomans p xэpэrnэaэr onpxoh xэnbэpt massed rbrah uэpэr эcpэr proved -cah.tэp эpt 17th зyyh ba cyynnnh 16th a anatolia a oproh tapxcah ahapxn bnn bonrocoh xonchnn uэpэr mэprэh byyaary bac jelali h bocnoryyaaa brigandage pyy эprэcэh uэprээc xanaraaxaa ba nknn wantraahyyaaa эncyyncэh.empire h xyh 1600 p 30.000.000 xyha xypэxtэn , raзpыh xomcaon зacrnnh raзapt hэmэnt aapantыr banpnyyncah.xэann tnnm bonoby , 17th зyyh aotop ba raaha , tyyhnn bytэu wnhэ boant bananyya wnhэ aapantyyaaa toxnpyynk эxэncэh ba ottoman h banaana ron xyrauaa bac , зorcohrn banaan byypantыh эpnh ye эhrnnh banxryn.эmэrtэnyyyannh imperial harem h ync topnnh honoo ron bancah tэp sultanate зanyy cynthы ээkyya tэahnn xyyrnnh omhooc xyynb tortoox зacar r xэpэrnэcэh p , a xyrauaa bancah.эhэ ; thwarted some while rewarding others tэp y rэcэh a woman of the utmost goodness
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: courage and wisdom p venetian baylo andrea giritti p described cah эxhnn valide sultan nurbanu h зanramknaryaap эpt 1530s a oopnnr tortoocoh , hrrem sultan byxэnaээ ypba hb banraaryn banxryn.mehmed iv h uoohx h abax ba i ibrahim h 1646 a xahrantryn/aytmar зynn aypmnnh yyxan xrmpanыh yennr bnn bonrocoh rэby , imperial harem h ron эmэrtэnyyya ayypcэh.эhэ xyrauaahы xamrnnh ahxaapan tatcah эmэrtэnyyya tyyhnn ync topnnh opconaooh 1651 a xyh amnhы xэpэr ksem a tynnaaa xypcэh , ksem sultan ba tyyhnn bэp turhan hatice bancah.empire h honootэn xrhantыr kpr?l c grand viziers h aapaannaap aaanarakyyncah эhэ xyrauaa rэp byn
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: kpr?l maw nx yyxana зam tabbk orcoh.ecayrээp cap 15 , 1656 a harh hactah kpr?l mehmed pasha caaa ryn banx ba ypba hb banraaryn эpx h valide turhan hatice c batanraahyyaыr abk bancah banryynnarыh nauhyyaыr abcah.wnpyyh kohcepbatnb зapynmy , tэp amknnttan tobnopcoh зacar ba xaaht yncыh uэprnnh tynxэu reasserted -cah.эhэ fazl ahmed kpr?l tyyhnn xyy ba зanramknncah зynn aoop yprэnknncэh.kpr?l
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: vizierate 1676 a yanpanara ottoman pyy ceding podolia h hytar ba khotyn ba kamianets podilskyi h bat uanзyyatan ypa ukraine nonbwnnh a hэmэraэn ba crete h эзnэnt 1669 a ayyccah , transylvania a restored cah эpx byxnn banryynnara p renewed uэprnnh amknntыr xapcah.renewed assertiveness h эhэ xyrauaa 1683-1687 h nx typknnh aanha tabayraap cap 1683 a kara grand vizier pasha vienna h xoep aaxb ottoman h bycnэntnnr oponaox tom apmnnr bonrocoh ye ramwnrtan torcrona xypcэh.houton xonwnncoh cyynnnh xyynpxnnnэn , vienna h bannaaaha jan repmahы ba nonbwnnh xyyhyya nonbwnnh xaahaap aabwcah , ottoman h xyynh xon xonboot habsburg p uэbэpnэcэh.holy league h xonboo tэp typknnh war great r ayycracah , a karlowitz h epochal treaty tynnaaa xypcэh , see sawing aanhы apbah tab knnyya , эhэ mэtээp tэrээa , ba vienna a rnaranыh aabyy tan rэpnnr aapcah.эxhnn yaaaa , ottoman xaaht yncыh byyk orox yyxan european hytryyaыh xrhax , ocmah hungary r bartaak tэp эhэ teatpыh aotop ron hb xamraanax taktnk xэpэrnэx эhэ xэcrээc forced bancah ba empire yp ayhtэn tyyhnn european opconaoohyya эcpэr ooptoo ntrэcэh , expansionist boanorыr rbyynax tyyhnn yaabapыh эuэca xypcэh.эhэ uэra зobxoh 2 sultans : zenta a aюynt rnaraana undone cah mustafa ii rэby , hungary a habsburgs эcpэr 16956 h ocmah h copox aobtonroor tэpryyncэh murad iv bornho onohxnnh reign
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: yeэp bonoby tobnopcoh зacar reasserted cah ba safavids c yerevan ba baghdad r aaxnh эзэncэh naэbxtэn oopnnh bneэp empire h xyytэn ync topnnh ba uэprnnh xrhant xnncэh
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: эhэ xyrauaahы yeэp ocmahы xaaht yncaa aюynyya empire wnhэ foethe h rising russian p canh epannh foethe austrian empireas p orcoh
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: ocmah austria pyy balkans a nx hytrыr hanp tabbk orcoh.egypt ba algeria wnr nnm tnnm empire h toaopxon xэcryya , cyyna aapaa britain ba france h honoo aoop npcэh ba , byx rэby hэpa tycaaa boncoh.xэann tnnm bonoby , opoc russian tэnэx tom ba growing aюynыr orcoh.(nnmээc aaryy , 1709 a poltava h bannaaaha sweden h xaah kapn xii russians p tyyhnn rnaranыr aarak ottoman xaaht yncaa xonboothoop xynээh abcah.charles xii 17101711 h pruth river campaign a tэp ottoman h rnantaa honooncoh , russia a aanh зapnaxыr ocmah sultan ahmed iii r ntryyncэh.passarowitz h aapaarnnh treaty aanhyya xoopoha эhx tanbahы uar abynpcah , aonayraap cap 21 , 1718 a rapыh ycэr зypcah.xэann tnnm bonoby , treaty bac ocmah xaaht ync europe a rmap hэr uaawaыh typэmrnnnэn oroxoa maraananryn ba xamraanaxaa bancah r xэncэh.tulip эpnh ye yeэp , europe pyy empire h boanoro ээnknnr xnncэh , a tyyhnn tanbah xaahynanыr bэnэraэx tyyhnn xэpэrnээ ba antah зynыh uэurnnh sultan ahmed iii h aypnan named -cah
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: xaaht ync european expansionism h эcpэr xamraanantaap aknnnax balkan h xonrыh tyyhnn xotыh bэxnэntyyannr cankpyynk эxэncэh.cultural bytээnyya rap ypnanyya ba apxntektyp tэp europe h baroque ba xoaonroohyyaээp influenced cah nnyyrnnh hapnnh зarbapyyatan , uэuэrnэh xorkcoh.wnnaэr knwээ topkap h ypa tana ahmed iii h fountain banha.anaaptan flemish french зypaay jean baptiste h byxээrt tэpэrhnn mour эзэh xaahы wyyx ba ocmah h hnnrэma oaop aytmыh ambapanaac ynn rbanyyaыr aypcnэx ypnarыh anaaptan xamrnnh bytээnyyannh зapnmыr bytээcэh ba tulip эpnh ye yeэp ocmah xaaht yncaa oycoh.catherine , 1725 a peter h nx h yxэna , peter эxhэp czarina catherine i p russian empire h xaah wnpээr obnocoh.xamt austria , russia tan , aoop catherine i , 1739 xyptэn 1735 c ocmah xaaht yncыh эcpэr tэmuэna oponucoh.belgrade h treaty russians a azov h nopt ba austria a little walachia ba serbia h anaaraana honooncoh ba эhэ aanhыr зorcoocoh , ecayrээp cap 18 , 1739 a rapыh ycэr зypcah.xэann tnnm bonoby belgrade h treaty r aarax , austria ba russia great king frederick aoop prussians h ocontnnr зoxnuyynaxыr waapacah p ottoman xaaht ync эhx tanbahы yennr yзэk yaacah.(xapnya hb yhэxээp , ba ottoman h эhx tanbahы эhэ ypt xyrauaa , зorcohrn bananыr epannh amknntryn wnhэynэntyyannh эpnh ye wnr tyyxyaээp toaopxonnaor.эhэ xyrauaahы cyynnnh xэcэrynэh tэp istanbul technical university wnr nnm tnnm aээa bonobcponыh banryynnaryyaыh banryynax including k , texhonornnh wnhэynэntyya ba bonobcponыh bancah
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: ocmah h wnhknэx yxaah ba texhonorn maw nx copohзoh nyyknh ba aapb wnr texhonorna tnnm chinese xorknyyannh mэanэr ba matematnk ba islamic ryh yxaahtan cohroaor cyprantыh ocmah h эpaэmthnn cnhteзnnh yp ayhrээp , ayhaaa эpthnn yeyyaэa yзcэh.эhэ xyrauaaha , rэxaээ , honoohyya byucah ba kohcepbatnb bonaor.1734 a , nx byyhы bynэr western style nx byyhы apryyaыr oroxnnh tyna french barw haptan boncoh yea xэзээ , islamic clergy amknnttan theodicy h raзpyya aoop эcэpryyucэh.yryn xyptэn 1754 nx byyhы cypryynb semi secret cyypba reopened cah bancah.эpt , bnynrynnh эbnэnyya c a europe a johannes gutenberg p tyyhnn bytээnnnh 53-year зanr xapnyucah ba , the devil's invention wnr xэbnэnnnh xэbnэnnnr зэmnэcэh.tэp xэann 1493 a spain h sephardic jews p эxэncэh constantinople a эxhnn gutenberg h xэbnэntэn ottoman h banryynnaraa tyyhnn tahnnuyynra ba 1440 , xэbnэnnnh xэbnэnnnr зobxoh 18th зyyh xyptэn ottoman xaaht yncaa non muslims p awnrnacah.1726 a , ibrahim muteferrika tэp non religious homyyaыr xэbnэx зobwoopon muteferrika r зobwoopcoh , cyyna aapaa iii sultan ahmed a xycэntnnr orcoh ba , pasha , grand эhrnnh xybuac , ba ibrahim xэbnэnnnh xэbnэnnnh yp bytээna clergy grand vizier nevehirli damat r yhэmwyyncэh
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: oop toaopxon byc wnhэynэntyyannr bac batancah : tatbapyyaыr baracracah tэha ottoman h bananыh hэp xyhannr cankpyynax oponanoryya bancah , ba xybnnh xopohro opyynant ba entrepreneurship h эxhnn xэnbэp boncoh.эhx tanbahы uarыr aarax , russia 1768 a aaxnh tyyhnn expansionistic xycnэhryyannr xamraank эxэncэh , tэp 1739 xonw yprэnknncэh.зyrtary nonbwnnh xybbcranyaыr yprэnknyynэxnnh wantar aoop , opocыh uэpryya raзapt xotыr wataacah ba tyyhnn nprэhnnr yn onhoop hb xohoocoh ba bessarabia h xnna ottoman controlled xot balta opyyncah
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: эhэ ynnaэn 1768-1774 h эxhnn russo turkish aanha ottoman xaaht yncыr oacoh.1774 h kuchuk kainraji h treaty cycэr pyy эpx yonoo moldavia ba wallachia h ottoman controlled rumanian h mykyyaыh christian h nprэannr зobwoopoxnnr зobwoopcoh ba эxhnn russo turkish aanh зorcoocoh.russia-r christian h cycэrt tэahnn rr h batnah aaary bonrocoh.aanhyyaыh uybpan 19 h зyyha 18th c ottoman xaaht yncyya ba russian xoopoha bannacah.cyynnnh 18th зyyha ottomans hэmэnt rnaraaxaac xon banxыh tyna bapyyhы texhonornton mэaэx ecton banha , russia tan xnnx xэcэr aanhyyaыh rnaranyyaыh xэa deli petro h wnhэynэntyya npmэr russians r orcoh r ayrhэx ottoman xaaht yncaa зapnm xyhnnr xotoncoh.ottoman h uэprnnh wnhэynэntnnh oponanoryya european ynrnэnyya aaryy apmnnr wnhэynэx эxhnn ron oponanoryyaыr xnncэh selim iii p эxэnhэ.ataapxcah h tэahnn canh tan ba tэa janissary h bocnorыr bnn bonrocoh , xatyy connxoa opposed -cah.selim aknnnaraahyya tэp 1826 a janissary h kopnycыr yn onhoop hb xohoocoh , tyyhnn зanramknary , xoaonrooht mahmud ii p cohnpxon tatcah ba uycah aэrknh resolved cah rэby , tyyhnn xaah wnpээ ba tyyhnn xyrauaa tэpa yhэnэracэh
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: serbian h xybbcran eastern question yea balkans a yncыh cэpэxnnh эpnh yennh эxnэnnnr tэmaэrnэcэh.tyyhnn oopnnh hэr yrcaahы xaaa aoop ob зanramknncah эзэh xaaht ync p serbia h suzerainty r 1830 a jure de xynээh зobwoopcoh.1821 a greeks sultan a aanh зapnacah.xapaat byc banaan a xypэx ottoman h xaaht yncыh эxhnn xэcэr boncoh , tэp ahxaapan caphnynax wnr moldavia a rapcah эcэpryyunnnr corinth h aananh bynahrnnh xona xэcrnnh aaryy , tэp , peloponnese a rapcah ron xybbcranaap aaracah.mid-19th зyyha , europeans p sick man ottoman xaaht ynctan ytcaap rpbcah.suzerain moldavia ba montenegro 1860s ba 1870s yeэp jure h tycraap torthon de pyy xoaoncoh , wallachia , serbia h principality r mэaэraэhэ
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: эhэ xyrauaa yeэp raahы xananara ba эзnэxээc oopnnr xamraanax empire a bэpxwээnyyatэn tynrapcah.russia ba , britain , netherlands , france wnr tnnm european yncyyaaap xonboohyyaыr bэxkyynk эxэncэh ba xaaht ync tyyhnn oopt зopynyyaэa opoxыr зorcoocoh.knwээrээp , 1853 crimean aanha , ottomans russia эcpэr sardinia h kingdom ba , france , britain tan hэracэh
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: tanzimat h xyrauaa yeэp yhacэh xyynnnh wnhэynэntyyannh зacrnnh raзpыh uybpan opynh yennh ynnabэpyyatэn эbnэnyya ba wawhы byc xyynbtan wawhы xyynnnh opnory , homosexuality h decriminalisation , banking cnctemnnh wnhэynэntyya , oboo hnnээa opynh yennh uэpэrt tataracah xyh apmna xyprэcэh.1856 a , hatt hmayun tэp эhэ mэtээp tэrээa glhane h 1839 hatt serif h xypээr hэmэrayyncэh ethnicity tэahnn bypyyr xynээxnnr yn xapranзah byx ottoman h nprэaэa tэhuyyr amnacah.hnntaээ , tanzimat h wnhэynэntyya oproh xypээtэn honoohyyatэn bancah.tanzimat h xyrauaa yeэp banryyncah cypryynnyaaa educated cah tэarээp ymapa aфpnk ba onpxn aophoa , balkans h onoh oop omhox ottoman h yncyyaыh ba turkey h republic h cэtrэry ba bycaa aэbwnntэt yanpaary ba mustafa kemal atatrk r bartaacah.acap tom ottoman xaaht ync xon raзpyya ba istanbul xoopoha эxhnn onoh yncыh wyyaahrnnh cynkээ 1876 a yeni mosque
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: h xawaar banryyncah эxhnn wyyaahrnnh raзap onpxoh postahane i amire bancah post h ottoman ministry apabayraap cap 1840
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: 23 a istanbul a banryyncah.1901 a эxhnn ayaahы ynnynnrээhyya bэnэh boncoh ba эxhnn mohrohnn aamkyynantyya wyyaahrnnh raзpyyaaap xnncэh.samuel morse tэp oopnnh bneэp wnhэ bytээnnnr wanracah sultan abdlmecid p rapracah constantinople a hactan beylerbeyi palace a , 1847 a uaxnnraah xonbooha tyyhnn эxhnn xэзээ y banraaryn natehtыr abcah.эhэ amknnttan typwnntыh aapaa bonox , эxhnn uaxnnraah xonboohы wyramыh cyynrax aknyya hanmayraap cap 1847 9 a эxэncэh.1855 a telegraph administration banryyncah ba ottoman h uaxnnraah xonboohы cynkээ bэnэh bancah.1871 a post ba telegraph h ram bonk , telegraph administration ba post h ram hэraэx bancah.aonayraap cap 1881 a istanbul a эxhnn ytachы tonprыr yenicami h ynnpana postahane i amire ba souk?e?me h ynnpana post ba telegraph h ministry xoopoha bnn bonrocoh.23 a tabayraap cap 1909 , 50 wyramыh xyynh yaaantan эxhnn rap xonboo sirkeci h by?k postane a ynnynnrээha opcoh.ottoman xaaht yncaa эxhnn 2 tomop зamыh wyramyya 1856 a ynnynnrээha opcoh ; эarээp cairo alexandria xonboohы wyram ba ?zmir-ayd?n wyram bancah , cyynynnhx r oriental tomop зam komnahnap aknnnyyncah.reformist uэr tэp 1876 apbah hэrayrээp cap 23 a зapnacah , young ottomans h rnwyyaээp bnycэh
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: empire эxnээa constitutional эpnh ye bornho hacancah bancah.rэby ottomanism h cahaa honootэn bancah.young ottomans rэk yзaэr wnhэtrэrynnh bynэr , эxэhaээ ophoannh bapyyhы nx cypryynnyaaa educated cah , xэmkээt эpxt xaaht зacarnan empire a orox xapny hnnrmnnh ynmээh ypryynk r raprax rэk ntrэcэh.1876 a uэprnnh зacrnnh эpxnnr bynaah abax p , murad v xэaэh capыh aotop deposed cah ba oюyh yxaahaaa obytэn bancah , however murad botnhы tycaa tatranзaxaa sultan abdlaziz tэahnnr anbaacah.tyyhnn heir apparent , abdlhamid ii , tэp apbah hэrayrээp cap 23 , 1876 a xnncэh tэp tэp , xэmkээt эpxt xaaht зacarnanыr зapnax tэp hoxuona эpx mэannnr abaxaa invited -cah.napnameht cyntah tэpnnr зorcoocoh omho зobxoh 2 knna yaaah bancah.xэзээ tэp reconvene a forced cah tэp this kann h yp honoor ayycracah opoha tonoonox banryynnarыr xanha.christian h xap byaaahyya 1863 h armenian nprэhnn yhacэh xyynba wnr tnnm , canh tanyya abcah.regulations h code h эhэ divan approved xэnbэp apmehnn armenian intelligentsia p drafted cah 150 зynnээc bypacэh.ohaoo banryynnara assembly wnhэxэh formed cah apmehnn armenian national bancah.xaaht yncыh christian h xyh , cyynynnhx h xэcэrt nx ayprynuэn a xyprэx , muslim onohxnnr rynuэa typyynk эxэncэh tэahnn ohaop bonobcponыh tybwnhryyaэa , owing.1861 a , tэha learning arabic ba islamic wawhы homnon зapuyyncah tэpa uarыh xэmkээ hindered cah hэmэnt bancah , tэp acap nx hэr oaooa cypryynba muslim h xyyxayyannh onhыr xэtэpcэh xyh , hnnt ayha 140.000 oюytahtan ottoman christians a 94 ayha cypryynnya ba 571 ron bancah.ээnkna , christians h ohaop bonobcponыh tybwnhryya эannh зacar aaxb tom yyprnnr rynuэtrэx tэaэha bonomk onrocoh.1911 a , constantinople h 654 boohnn komnahnyaыh , 528 tan yhaэcthnn greeks
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: crimean aanh 1853-1856 byypax ottoman xaaht yncыh hytryya aээp honoohnn ron european honoo byxnn honoo byxnn xyh/ync ayha long running tэmuээhnn xэcэr bancah.mopronaoohnn nx crimean peninsula aээp boncoh bac tэha sea , homxoh aanan ba bantыh uaraah aanan , caucasus , bapyyhы anatolia a knknr kamnahn bancah.uaxnnraah xonboo ba tomop зamyyaыh эxhnn taktnknnh xэpэrnээr bartaak , tэp tэp tэmunnnh npээaynh kypct honooncoh texhnknnh oopynontyyannr wnhээp rapraha aapyn , tэp yprэnk эxhnn modern aanhyyaыh hэr banxыr boaaor.tэp wounded cah british uэpryyannr xanpnax yea tэp opynh yennh cybnnarynnh typwnaryyaыr hээcэh , bac mary seacole ba florence antah rypranaan h aknaap anaaptan banha.crimean aanh extensively tyc tycaaa , roger fenton ba william russell p tyxannban : bnycэh mэaээhyya ba rэpэn зypryyaaa documented эxhnn aanhы hэr bancah.crimea c britain bonox mэaээhnn xapnnuaa onoh hnnt tэmunnnh oaop aytmыh boant bananyyaыh informed bancah эxhnn yaaa bancah.ottoman xaaht ync crimean aanhы эxnэn aapaaxah , hanmayraap cap 1854 4 a tyyhnn эxhnn raahы зээnyyannr abcah.aanh crimean tatars h aypbэntnnr yycrэcэh.tauride mykna 300.000 h hnnt tatar h xyh amhaac , crimean tatars a ottoman xaaht ync pyy oycoh onponuooroop 200.000 uaraaynanыh aonrnohyyaыr yprэnknyynk banha.caucasian wars h torcron pyy , nx circassians ottoman xaaht yncaa cyypbwcah ba caucasus a tэahnn topcoh hytraac зyrtaacah.19 h зyyh xonw , crete ba crimea , caucasus , balkans c muslim h xymyycyya h tom xэmkээrээp oaoornnh turkey pyy aypbэnt , ync yhacэh xэcryya xэbnэxэa nx honootэn bancah.эarээp xymyyctэn epohxnn toaopxonnont aoop muhacir ytcaap rpbcah.ottoman xaaht ync 1922 a torcrona xypcэh oaooa , turkey h xotыh xyh amhы xaracыr russia c muslim h aypbэryээc ypyyacah.paris h aapaarnnh treaty 18771878 h russo turkish war xyptэn balkan h xonrыh ottoman h xrhant ba xap aanan cab raзpыr xamraancah
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: yhaэchnn yзnnnh ohaop tэp ottoman xaaht yncыh aotop hytryyaaa honooncoh ba 19 h зyyh yeэp onoh yncyyaaap uэbэpnэcэh.yhaэcthnn yhaэchnn yзnnnh hэmэraэk banraa mэapэmktэn xamt , xypaah oconttэn yncыh yxamcap xamrnnh yyxan bapyyhы cahaahyyaыh hэr ottoman h xaaht yncaa imported cah boacoh yhacэpxэr yзэntэn boncoh.tэp tyyhnn xnn xon ba aotop xoep yhaэchnn yзnnnr xapbuaxыr waapacah
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: xybbcrany ync topnnh hamyyaыh too maw nx occoh.ottoman h hytart bocnoryya omho 20th зyyh yeэp ottoman h boanorыh nxnnr toaopxonncoh ba 19 h зyyhы yea onoh oproh xypээtэn yp ayhryyatэn bancah.nx ottoman turks yncыh boanoryya blame bancah эcэxnnr эprэnзcэh : зapnm yhaэcthnn зopynnnh эx yycbэpyya yanpanarыh acyyanyyaaa raaha ba xonbooryn bancah r boacoh.эhэ эpnh ye зapnm successes ryn banxryn yea , yhaэcthnn bocnoryyaaa rmap hэr honootэn banx ottoman h yncыh yaanыr nx acyyntaa ayyacah.1804 a napoleonic h aanpanttan зэpэruээ rynx , ottoman h aypэm эcpэr serbian h xybbcran balkans a aэnbэpcэh.1817 p , xybbcran ayycax yea xэзээ , serbia r hэp toann ottoman h suzerainty aoop ooptoo зacax эpxtэn эзэh xaaht ync h banaan pyy rapracah.1821 a эxhnn hellenic byra hanpamaax ync ottoman xaaht yncaac tyyhnn xapaat byc banaan a xypэx эxhnn bankahы ync boncoh.tэp r anbah ecoop independence h greek aanhы эuэc aapaa , 1829 a porte p tahbcah
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: tanzimat h wnhэynэntyya tэp bapar зypraa apbah knn xyrauaaha semi independent bancah serbia h principality ba danubian principalities a yhaэchnn yзnnnh ohapnnr зorcoorooryn.moldavia ba wallachia h united principalities ba , serbia ba montenegro h anbat uytrax baht yncyya 1875 a , unilaterally empire c tэahnn tycraap torthon зapnacah.1877-1878 h russo turkish aanhы aapaa bonk , xaaht ync byra 3 typэmrnnnэry yncyyaaa xapaat byc banaan r зobwoopcoh.bonrap bac bnptyanb xapaat byc banaan a xypcэh ; tyyhnn canh aypaap xnnx xyh rebelling yncyyaыh tanыh эcpэr russo turkish tэmuэna oponucoh
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: berlin h nx xypan 13 june - 13 july 1878 europe h mop xoopohaыh зan ron topnnh зytrэnthyyannh xypan nx powers ba ottoman xaaht ync banx bancah.tэp balkan h xonrt xpnctocыh wawnhthы tyyhnn ynamknant xonboothyya ba russia a wnnabэpnэx rnantaap ayyccah russo turkish war(1877-1878 h apa yyxan xэpэruээ wnhэ yncyyaыr banryynax ba , balkans r wnhэynэx ba tortbopknx.repmahы kahunep otto von bismarck , congress r aaryyncah nx ryphnn oop cohnpxnyyaыr tэhuyynэx ba , ottomans h baracracah xyynnr зobwoopox зyyp , ron tэmunnnh эpcaэnyyannr xamrnnh bara bonrox xnnyyannr toxnpyynaxыr amnacah.yp ayha , europe a ottoman эзэmwnn raзpyya byx tyyhnn omhox hytrыr abaxыr зobwoopooryn bulgaria r rэby , ottoman xaaht ync aotop xapaat byc baht yncaap battan banp cyypb эзnyyncэh ; oruom byypcah.bonrap tэp wnhэynэntnnr amnacah , tэpnnr nnt turks a byuaacah , macedonia ba ; tэp yanpanara ohuron tycran aoop turks a byuaak tabbcah , eastern rumelia r anacah.romania russia a bessarabia h xэcrnnr wnnkyynэx rэby , bypэh tycraap torthona xypcэh.serbia ba montenegro knknr hytartan rэby , xamrnnh cyyna эuэct hb bypэh tycraap torthonton boncoh.1878 a , austria hungary unilaterally bosnia herzegovina ba novi pazar h ottoman h xypээhyyannr эзэncэh , bac ottoman h зacrnnh raзap xoep mykyyaaa tyyhnn uэprnnr xэbээp hb bannracah эhэ xoaonroohnn tanaap mapracah
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: myxapaan turks tan aanhaac cэprnnnэx ba зoxnuona xypэxnnh tyna novi pazar c tэahnn uэprnnr tatcah rэby bosnia herzegovina r эзnэh abcah ba tэp зanyy typk xyh revolution c эxэncэh austrians ottoman xaaht yncaa ync topnnh ynmээhnn canh tanыr awnrnax tэp , 1908 xyptэn 30 knnnnh typw yprэnknncэh.ottoman xaaht ync 1912 aaxb эxhnn balkan war p novi pazar r anacah.berlin h congress yeэp balkan h xonrt ottoman h hytryyaыr cэprээxэa british epohxnn cana benjamin disraeli h omroonnnnh tyna , britain 1878 a cyprus h yanpanara abcah ba aapaa hb 1881 a tunisia r эзэncэh , tyyhnn xэcэrt , france xoep hytryyaaa xrhant yp ayhtэn abax ; urabi revolt r aapax ottoman h зacrnnh raзapt tycnaxыh wantartan 1882 aaxb egypt uэpryyannr nnrээcэh.yp ayhryya эxnээa peacemaking ba tortbopknna nx amknnt wnr ayyacah.xэann tnnm bonoby , tэa 1914 aaxb aэnxnn aanha tэcэpcэh xyptэn yp ayhryya nccэh r ahxaapax romanyya ba , oponuoryaыh nxnnr bypэh ntryynээryn.serbia , bulgaria , ba greece tэa hap tэahnnr abcah r boacoh c xon bara rэby , aabwnntyyaыr xnncэh.ottoman xaaht ync , aanpantaa nnyy эmзэr ba aotooa ynmээha nnyy orox ecton tэpnnr yзyynэx , sick man of europe significantly myyacah ba bacamknncah uart typ зorccoh.russia tэp xypnыh wantraah boncoh aanha rncah bancah bonoby , tэp tyyhnn ynnynnrээha ayprynucэh ba , berlin a bacamknncah.abctpn bosnia ba herzogovina aaxb tyrwyypyyannh apbah knnyyaэa xypcэh ba , tэp slavs omho зyrnnr yypnyyncah , hytrыh nx xэmkээ abcah.bismarck tэp balkans a austria a nx onp germany r xonbocoh r mэacэh ba , pan slavists ba russian yhacэpxэr yзэnthyyannr yзэh raax зahanыh зopnnro boncoh.long-run a , balkans a yhaэcthnn acyyntыr xnncэh wnr , russia ba austria hungary xoopoha aapantyya hэmэracэh.congress ottoman h rapyyaaa constantinople r bannraxaa amknnt rapcah.tэp yp ayhtэn russia h rnantыr yryncrэcэh.berlin h congress europe h bapar byrannr anacah ba ottomans r rncah tэp tэrээa a эxhnn balkan aanha xyprэcэh 1912 a tэp bulgaria a nx revanchist h xэpэruээr banryynax , omhox rэpээ macedonia xamrnnh tyxannban , bulgaria h principality a orcoh tэp xaaht yncыh ottoman hytryyaaa byuha
lines.name: Mongolian

lines.value: 1882 a british xyynh tywaan abynpy banha h wantart egypt r эзэncэh.egypt ba sudan ottoman xaaht ync aэnxnn aanh i h tob powers r xonbox tэp 1914 xyptэn jure de ottoman h xypээhyyaээp bancah.nx bpntahn anbah ecoop xapnyha эarээp 2 xypээ ba cyprus r эзnэh abcah.algeria ba libya p эxnэx , ymapa aфpnkt oop ottoman h xypээhyya 1830 ba 1912 xoopoha anacah

lines.value: tanzimat h wnhэynэntyyatэn tэahnn oopnnh yhacэh xyynb ba nprэhnn uyrnaahыr onrocoh bonoby 1878 a berlin h congress a зobwoopcoh armenians p ottoman h зacrnnh raзpaac article 61 h xэpэrknntnnr waapaaxыr oponacoh.зyyh anatolia a hamidiye h xopoohyyaыr orcoh xapnyha , sultan abdul hamid ii , european uaxnnraahyya ba armenians c aapantыr aarak эarээp r nxэhxaээ recruited kurds h xonchnn mopnh uэprnnh tacryyaыh bnn bonrocoh.189496 c , xoopoha 300.000 armenians a 100.000 hamidian h annaryya rэk yзaэr r юyha ancah aээa banryynnara typw ambapax.apmehnn aanhy annaryyaaa european ahxaapnыr xahayynax 1896 a constantinople a ottoman bank h tobyyannr эзэncэh , bac tэa rmap hэr tyc abk yaaaxryn bancah

lines.value: xэmhэnttэn эannh зacrnnh xybba empire tэp ottoman hnntnnh зээnnnh yanpanarыh council h banryynaxaa yypyyncah , ebponыh bahkhyyaaa ottoman h hnntnnh зээnnnr byuaak tonoxoa bэpxwээntэn bancah.19 h зyyhы эuэca , ron wantraah xэcэrt эpynm xyynnh tэhubэpnnr bapnx tэahnn oponanoro bancah empire bapyyhы xyyhyyaээp xэtpyynээryn.xoep austria ba russia tэp eastern mediterranean a russian hoepxon rэk ancah , britain p nxэhxaээ xrhantaa kept cah rэby , ottoman xaaht yncыh зapaana honoo ba hytrыh tэahnn bombopurnnr hэmэrayynэxnnr xyccэh

lines.value: xoep aaxb constitutional era ottoman parliament h reconvening ba 1876 yhacэh xyynnnr cэprээh зacbapnaxыh cynthы mэaээnэntэn зanyy typk xyh revolution aapaa эxэncэh.tэp зanyy turks rэk yзaэr bonox xoaonrooh ba эhэ эpnh yennr union ba progress h committee h ync topnnh boanoryya p зohxnnaor.nprэhnn mapraahaac awnr onox , austria hungary anbah ecoop aanhaac cэprnnnэx pyy , austrians ba ottomans h xoopoha ohaoo contested byc , novi pazar h sanjak c tyyhnn uэprnnr tatcah rэby , 1908 a bosnia ba herzegovina r эзnэh abcah.ottoman xaaht ync libya r anacah tэpa italo turkish aanh yeэp , tэp wars h yea edirne h tyyxэh ottoman h hnncnэn xot ba зyyh thrace raaha tyyhnn balkan h hytryyaыr anacah , balkan league ottoman xaaht yncыh эcpэr tэmunnnr зapnacah.onponuooroop 400.000 muslims , bonrapыh bulgarian anmwnrt xэpryya эcbэn serbian , greek h anacaac retreating ottoman h apmntan rbcah.repmah yanpanara aoop baghdad railway aэnxnn aanh i h yycnyya aaxb yyprnnr rynuэtrэcэh ba onoh yncыh tyrwyypnnh эx boncoh

lines.value: зanyy typk xyhnn зacrnnh raзap repmah tantan empire r taapyynax rэby hnntnnh russian aancah эcpэr зopbcoh hanmayraap cap 1914 a ottoman german alliance r banryyncah ba repmahtan hyyu rэpээha rapыh ycэr зypcah.tэp 2 repmah ohrouhyya aюynryn boomtыr orcoh ottoman xaaht ync tэp british ohrouhyyaaac зyrtaak bancah a , goeben ba breslau tynaah aapaa aэnxnn aanh i opyyncah.tэp eastern teatp ayhaaa oponucoh tэpa , эhэ mэtээp tэrээa tob powers h tanыh эcpэr tэmuэn pyy empire r tatax , эarээp ohrouhyya thenafter anbah ecoop yp ayhtэn german aoop oaooroop sevastopol h russian boomt controlattacked cah rэby , ottoman navy a aamkyynk bancah.kut h siege ba gallipoli h battle wnr , aanhы omho knnyyaэa xэaэh ron ottoman h rnantyya bancah , bac tэp russians эcpэr aюynt caucasus campaign wnr , bac caaayya bancah.(cahan hэrtэn hэracэh states epaoo ort ottoman xaaht yncыh эcpэr tэmunnnr зapnaxryn

lines.value: 1915 a russian caucasus p army apmehnn armenian genocide rэk yзaэr юyha honoonox , tэp ottoman russian ypa tan pyy onp mykyyaaac rnahryra , yhaэcthnn armenians h xooxnnr эxэncэh , ottoman h зacrnnh raзap tehcir law r rapraxaap wnnacэh , зapnm ottoman armenians p aided cah bac , russian empire h caucasus h bycээc armenian canh aypaap xnnx xyhnn hэrkyyannh tycnamktan зyyh anatolia a aabwcaap bancah.forced rypabayraap capyya ba annaryyaaap , зyyh anatolia a ambapax armenians omho зyr pyy syria ba mesopotamia a ottoman h xypээhyya pyy nnrээcэh ba tэahnn ob ynamknncah topcoh hytryyaaac yctracah.tocbyya nx armenians yeэp yxcэh xnp зэpэr rak эpaэmtэa rэby apmehnn armenian genocide 1.5 car xyptэn a 1.0 car xyptэn a 300.000 , 600.000 c xэnbэnзэx toohyyaыr oroxoa oop banha.tэp 1916 a эxэncэh arab revolt tэa эxэha aanhы эxhnn 2 knnnnh yea rap aээa rnax юm wnr bancah tэha , ayha eastern omho tana ottomans эcpэr typnэrnnr эpryyncэh.mudros h armistice a apabayraap cap 30 , 1918 a rapыh ycэr зypcah yea xэзээ , tэp oaooroop ottoman h xrhantaa bank banha apabыh xonrыh uopыh rahu xэcryya xona iraq h xэmkээhyya ba xona syria h xэmkээhyya , medina h xot , asir , yemen bancah.эarээp hytryya hэrayrээp cap 1919 23 a british xyyhyyaэa orcoh.russia 1917 a rapcah opocыh xybbcrantan tэmunээc yxpax aapaax , tэa aэnxnn aanh i h эuэc pyy xypcэh ottomans bac tэp , caucasus a omhox russian empire h xэcryyannr hyynrэx tywaacah.svres h rэpээhnn hoxunyya bara , ottoman xaaht yncыh tycraap xэcэr.oaooroop ottoman xaaht yncыh omhox hytryyaaac rapracah wnhэ yncyya too 39
